desc: Handles the movement speed of flying entities such as parrots and bees.

name: JUMP_STRENGTH

name: ATTACK_KNOCKBACK
desc: Handles additional horizontal knockback when damaging another entity.

name: DEFAULT_SKIN_LOCATION

name: isBootstrapped
desc: Whether the blocks, items, etc have already been registered

name: resultSlots
desc: The inventory slot that stores the output of the crafting recipe.

name: lastHurt
desc: Damage taken in the last hit. Mobs are resistant to damage less than this for a short time after taking damage.

name: lastHurtMobTimestamp
desc: Holds the value of ticksExisted when setLastAttacker was last called.

name: targetConditions
desc: This filter is applied to the Entity search. Only matching entities will be targeted.

name: ZERO
desc: An immutable BlockPos with zero as all coordinates.

name: columnType

name: columnHeight

name: deleteLayerButton
desc: The remove layer button

name: minDirtyX

name: maxDirtyY
desc: The highest dirty z value

name: maxDirtyX
desc: The highest dirty x value

desc: True if changes have been made to {@link #loadedChunks} and thus a new copy of the collection has to be made into {@link #immutableLoadedChunks}.

name: toDrop
desc: Chunks that have been requested to be unloaded, but haven't been unloaded yet.

name: entitiesInLevel
desc: Chunk positions in this set have fully loaded and their TE's and entities are accessible from the world

name: updatingChunkMap
desc: Chunks in memory. This should only ever be manipulated by the main thread.

name: visibleChunkMap
desc: Same as {@link #loadedChunks}, but immutable for access from other threads. This should never be mutated.

name: isSigning
desc: Determines if the signing screen is open

name: isModified
desc: Whether the book's title or contents has been modified since being opened

name: lastClickTime
desc: In milliseconds

name: frameTick
desc: Update ticks since the gui was opened

name: blocks
desc: Hardcoded set of blocks this tool can properly dig at full speed. Modders see instead.

name: destId
desc: The entity that is holding the leash, or -1 to clear the holder.

name: mob
desc: The entity that this goal belongs to

name: items
desc: The items currently placed in the slots of the brewing stand.

name: INVALID_CHUNK_POS
desc: Value representing an absent or invalid chunkpos

name: lastHit
desc: After punching the stand, the cooldown before you can punch it again without breaking it.

name: blockPos
desc: Block to move to

name: nextStartTick
desc: Controls task execution delay

name: location
desc: The location of the resource within the registry.

name: registryName
desc: The name of the parent registry of the resource.

name: channel
desc: The active channel

name: packetListener
desc: The PacketListener instance responsible for processing received packets

name: address
desc: The address of the remote party

name: disconnectedReason
desc: A Component indicating why the network has shutdown.

name: queue
desc: The queue for packets that get sent before the channel is connected.\nEvery tick or whenever a new packet is sent the connection will try to flush this queue, if the channel has since finished connecting.

name: INGREDIENT
desc: The fuel item used to make the minecart move.

name: DISPENSER_REGISTRY
desc: Registry for all dispense behaviors.

name: toItem

name: primaryPower

desc: A list of effects that beacons can apply.

desc: A list of beam segments for this beacon.

name: secondaryPower
desc: The secondary effect given by this beacon.

name: name
desc: The custom name for this beacon.

name: levels
desc: The number of levels of this beacon's pyramid.

name: defaultModifiers
desc: Modifiers applied when the item is in the mainhand of a user.

name: chunks
desc: Chunks that are at most {@link #range} chunks away from the closest player.

name: ALL_BLOCKS
desc: A list of all valid block states.

name: horse

name: yMouse

name: xMouse
desc: The mouse x-position recorded during the last rendered frame.

name: normal

name: oppositeIndex
desc: Index of the opposite Direction in the VALUES array

name: data3d
desc: Ordering index for D-U-N-S-W-E

name: BY_2D_DATA
desc: All Facings with horizontal axis in order S-W-N-E

name: data2d
desc: Ordering index for the HORIZONTALS field (S-W-N-E)

name: random

name: pathToPosition
desc: Current path navigation target

name: highlightPos

desc: Determines the cost per entity towards the maximum spawn cap.

desc: Determines the total amount of entities that can spawn in a location based on their current cost (e.g. a cost of 0.1 and a max total of 1 means at most ten entities can spawn in the given location).

name: yesButton
desc: The text shown for the first button in GuiYesNo

name: noButton
desc: The text shown for the second button in GuiYesNo

name: tick

name: lastNanoTime
desc: Time in nanoseconds of when the class is loaded

name: frameTimer
desc: The FrameTimer's instance

name: blockRenderer
desc: The BlockRenderDispatcher instance that will be used based off gamesettings

name: connectedToRealms
desc: True if the player is connected to a realms server

name: profileProperties

name: pendingTarget

name: progressO

name: extending
